missigness_impute_factors_interactions.Rd

compute per group averages and impute values should generalize at some stage

missigness_impute_factors_interactions(
  pdata,
  config,
  probs = 0.03,
  value = c("long", "nrReplicates", "nrMeasured", "meanArea", "imputed"),
  add.prefix = FALSE,
  global = TRUE
)

Arguments

pdata

data.frame

config

AnalysisConfiguration

probs

quantile to take average from (default 0.1)

value

use default

add.prefix

use default

See also

Other imputation: UpSet_interaction_missing_stats(), aggregate_contrast(), get_contrast(), missigness_histogram(), missingness_per_condition_cumsum(), missingness_per_condition()

#> Column added : nr_peptide_Id_IN_protein_Id
stopifnot(nrow(bb$data) == 25780)

data <- bb$data
